'''天主教霍洛宗座代牧區'''（{{lang-la|Vicariatus Apostolicus Ioloensis}}）是[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[宗座代牧區|宗座代牧區]]，直屬[[聖座|聖座]]<ref>{{cite web |title=《天主教法典》第二編 |url=https://www.vatican.va/chinese/cic/cic-libro-II-ParteII-cann330-572_zh-t.pdf |publisher=聖座 |accessdate=2020-04-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405064704/https://www.vatican.va/chinese/cic/cic-libro-II-ParteII-cann330-572_zh-t.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-05 |language=zh-hant |dead-url=no }}</ref>，管轄[[蘇祿省|蘇祿省]]和[[塔威塔威省|塔威塔威省]]。

當地以[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]信徒為主，天主教徒佔極少數。宗座代牧區於2010年時有28,937名教友，佔總人口2.6%。由12名司鐸服務5個堂區。宗座代牧區的主教座堂是[[霍洛|霍洛]]{{link-en|嘉模山聖母主教座堂 (霍洛)|Our Lady of Mount Carmel Cathedral, Jolo|嘉模山聖母主教座堂}}。現任宗座代牧為{{link-de|嘉祿·因森|Charlie Inzon|嘉祿·M·因森}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 04.04.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/04/200404b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-04-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404133142/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/04/200404b.html |archivedate=2020-04-04 |language=en |date=2020-04-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

'''蘇祿宗座監牧區'''於1953年10月28日設立。<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=XXI |year=1954 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=66-67 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-46-1954-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405044106/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-46-1954-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-05 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>宗座監牧區於1958年7月12日升為宗座代牧區並易名<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=III |volume=I |year=1959 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=319-320 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-51-1959-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405045239/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-51-1959-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-05 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

